<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-03-29T13:29:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-03-29T13:29:00-05:00" n="150" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d150">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 861.00/1401</note>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Russia</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_FDR1" type="from"><hi rend="italic">Francis</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi></head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Extract]<note n="2" xml:id="d150fn2">Printed in full in <ref target="frus1918Russiav01#pg_488">vol. <hi rend="smallcaps">i</hi>, p. 488</ref>.</note></seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Vologda</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-03-29T21:00:00+02:31"><hi rend="italic">March 29,
                                            1918, 9 p.m.</hi></date>
                                    <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received March 30, 7.50
                                    p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>Moscow press prints to-day: “American Consul informed Supreme
                                Economic Council that American Government agrees to resume
                                commercial and industrial relations with Russia, regardless of
                                repudiation of debts.” Suppose Department authorized such statement,
                                if made. …</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed><persName corresp="#p_FDR1"><hi rend="smallcaps">Francis</hi></persName></signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>